索尼英语VTuber项目“PRISM Project”结束https://www.moguravr.com/prism-project-end/井文 Mon, 04 Mar 2024 01:43:38 +0000VTuber https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247151 <p>索尼运营的面向英语国家的 VTuber 项目 PRISM Project 宣布其活动将于 2024 年 3 月 31 日结束。从 4 月 1 日起，所有目前加入的 VTuber（总共 18 人）将保留他们的名字和“角色”。</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/prism-project-end/">索尼的英语 VTuber 项目“PRISM Project”结束的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>索尼运营的面向英语国家的 VTuber 项目<a href="https://www.prismproject.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PRISM Project</a>宣布将于 2024 年 3 月 31 日结束活动。所有目前隶属的 VTuber（总共 18 人）将从<strong>4 月 1 日起转变为个人 VTuber，保留他们的姓名和“角色”</strong> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-247153" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1.webp" alt="" width="1350" height="1350" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1.webp 1350w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/13546-3788-aeee2216441903fab9ef97631add6a1b-1500x1500-1-768x768.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1350px) 100vw, 1350px" /></a></p><p> “PRISM Project”是AnotherBall Co., Ltd.于2021年推出的项目。成员是来自2120年未来的组织成员，主要活跃在YouTube上。该业务于 2022 年转移至索尼音乐娱乐公司 (SME)，此后该公司一直负责管理该项目。</p><p>属于“PRISM项目”的VTuber成为个人VTuber后，其当前的外观和各种帐户（X、YouTube等）的权利将被转移。每位成员计划于3月份在各自的频道上解释他们未来的活动政策。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en"> 【PRISM项目停止运营公告】</p><p>尊敬的 PRISMers，感谢大家的支持。PRISM 项目将于 2024 年 3 月 31 日停止运营。https <a href="https://t.co/XggbVLGeKE">://t.co/XggbVLGeKE</a> <a href="https://t.co/OCdCx8ATJh">pic.twitter.com/OCdCx8ATJh</a></p><p> — 棱镜项目 (@PRISMproj) <a href="https://twitter.com/PRISMproj/status/1763776242468139244?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 3 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>根据公告，原定3月份的活动将如期举行。各种商品的销售将于3月31日结束。虽然《PRISM Project》的官方 YouTube 频道和 X 账号将不再更新，但仍会作为档案继续发布。</p><p> （参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/PRISMproj/status/1763776242468139244" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X（旧推特）</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/prism-project-end/">索尼的英语 VTuber 项目“PRISM Project”结束的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
泰国VTuber热潮目前陷入困境，追逐“文化熔炉”诞生的新人https://www.moguravr.com/the-kingdom-of-thailand-vtuber/すら Fri, 01 Mar 2024 10:00:25 +0000 VTuberARPタイ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247054 <p>自“虚拟YouTuber”一词首次使用以来已经过去了七年多，VTuber文化在日本从年轻人到老年人广泛传播。这种VTuber文化正在逐渐向海外传播，体现了每个国家的独特个性[…]</p><p>这篇文章首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/the-kingdom-of-thailand-vtuber/">，讲述了从泰国 VTuber 热潮如火如荼的“文化熔炉”中涌现出来的新人才的故事</a>。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-1024x768.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-1024x768.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-768x576.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ahx5m7ljohxl-jpg.webp 1215w" width="1024" height="768" /></a></p><p>自“虚拟YouTuber”一词首次使用以来已经过去了七年多，VTuber文化在日本从年轻人到老年人广泛传播。这种VTuber文化正在逐渐向海外传播，并开始体现每个国家的独特个性。</p><p>在华语国家，类似于日本氛围的VTuber文化已经扎根，而在英语国家，像VShojo这样尊重个性的文化正在形成。在拉丁美洲，独立VTuber（个人VTuber）的存在更为突出，而在韩语国家，具有浓厚K文化的音乐团体在国内外越来越受欢迎。</p><p>由于语言障碍，你可能没有太多机会每天看到这些 VTuber 文化。泰王国特别受欢迎，但知名度并不高。泰国的一个团体已经开始引起国内外的关注，目前正在成为一个非常热门的场景。</p><p>这次我想谈谈泰国深厚的VTuber文化。</p><h2 id="h.7fw8butz1gmd">从数据看与泰国的关系</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-1024x547.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-1024x547.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-300x160.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-768x410.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.l47sjf9finpt-jpg.webp 1535w" width="1024" height="547" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.mofa.go.jp/mofaj/press/pr/wakaru/topics/vol154/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.mofa.go.jp/mofaj/press/pr/wakaru/topics/vol154/index.html</a></p><p>虽然我对国际事务不太熟悉，但我想简单谈谈迄今为止日本和泰国的关系。日本和泰国不是朋友，两国已保持<a href="https://www.mofa.go.jp/mofaj/press/pr/wakaru/topics/vol154/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">外交关系130多年</a>。</p><p>经济上，两国保持友好关系。例如， <a href="https://www.careerlinkfactory.co.jp/blog/thai-employment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国的日本餐馆数量不断增加</a>， <a href="https://www.clisk.com/web-marketing/thailand-inbound-promotion-20230823" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国游客数量据说是东南亚最多的</a>。此外，在日本工作的泰国工人数量是 <a href="https://www.careerlinkfactory.co.jp/blog/thai-employment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">所有国家中最多的之一</a>。从这些方面来看，可以说日本和泰国之间的联系非常牢固。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u3kqh2utmhyi-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/vbSfqmS7va4?t=656" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://youtu.be/vbSfqmS7va4?t=656</a></p><p>从文化角度来看，泰国和日本有着密切的关系。漫画就是一个例子。可以毫不夸张地说，20世纪80年代，<a href="https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1520009409094625280" target="_blank" rel="noopener">日本漫画渗透到泰国青年文化中</a>，成为构成当今日泰关系的元素之一。</p><p>根据集英社运营的海外服务“MANGA Plus by SHUEISHA”的<a href="https://youtu.be/vbSfqmS7va4?t=656" target="_blank" rel="noopener">读者统计</a>，泰国的用户数量排名第二。考虑到<a href="https://www.unfpa.org/data/world-population-dashboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国的人口大约排在世界第20位</a>，你可以看到日本漫画和泰国之间的紧密联系。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1xvj9khmgrth-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="575" /></a><br /> <a href="https://trends.google.co.jp/trends/explore?date=today%205-y&amp;geo=TH&amp;q=%2Fg%2F11byz8037n,%2Fg%2F11hznck6gj,%2Fm%2F0w68qx3,%2Fg%2F11f7r5y9lz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://trends.google.co.jp/trends/explore?date=today%205-y&amp;geo=TH&amp;q=%2Fg%2F11byz8037n、%2Fg%2F11hznck6gj、%2Fm%2F0w68qx3、%2Fg%2F11f7r5y9lz</a></p><p>然而，请记住，虽然日本内容在泰国很受欢迎，但它并不是单方面消费的。当我观看泰国VTuber的直播和视频时，我经常看到不仅来自日本，而且来自亚洲、英语国家和其他地区的文化共存。这种文化被泰国VTuber行业人士形容为“<a href="https://premium.kai-you.net/article/759" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文化熔炉</a>”，也赋予了泰国视频文化独特的魅力。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.n7jzd1jqodp1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://streamscharts.com/news/vtubers-viewership-q1-2023-japanese-streamers-continue-lead" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://streamscharts.com/news/vtubers-viewership-q1-2023-japanese-streamers-continue-lead</a></p><p>从VTuber的角度来看，还有一些有趣的数据。根据收集分发平台收视数据的“Streams Charts”发布的《 <a href="https://streamscharts.com/news/vtubers-viewership-q1-2023-japanese-streamers-continue-lead" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2023年第一季度VTuber直播收视率</a>》报告显示，泰国在VTuber分发方面排名第三。</p><p>当然，这就提出了如何确定VTuber的国籍的问题，但这个统计数据很有趣。虽然这不包括中文平台，但这对我来说是一个令人惊讶的结果，因为英语、中文、西班牙语和韩语在 YouTube 和 Twitch 上一直很突出。不过，如果与<a href="https://twitter.com/VRchama/status/1622262309703024644" target="_blank" rel="noopener">专门收集东南亚VTuber信息的Valentino Ringo的统计数据相比，泰国是仅次于印度尼西亚的第二大国家</a>，就可以看出Streams Charts的数据是正确的。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-jpg.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.756t2veb7oi7-300x168.webp 300w" width="768" height="431" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jtfwOCBx-Qs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jtfwOCBx-Qs</a></p><p>泰国也是催生VTuber文化的Kizuna AI最早走红的地方。它始于泰国，并迅速传播到从韩国到美国的世界各地。 <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20230607083800/https://entamejin.com/column/archives/4396" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Activ8 Co., Ltd. 首席执行官 Takeshi Osaka 的采访</a>中也谈到了这一点。</p><p>这不仅限于VTuber，近年来在音乐等其他内容中也可以看到类似的趋势。通过东南亚传播到世界各地的时尚似乎已成为一种趋势。</p><h2 id="h.13rug9540i3f">早期：从游戏解说到VTuber</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-jpg.webp 640w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.j5otpnugtc55-300x169.webp 300w" width="640" height="360" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbFgtVZikM8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbFgtVZikM8</a></p><p>泰国的 VTuber 历史有着非常深厚的渊源。</p><p>例如，“TheQuillmon”是在藤崎悠亚的影响下<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbFgtVZikM8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">开始的第一个泰国VTuber</a>而闻名。在活动初期，我并没有称自己为VTuber。他从<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_slvmwj2OnM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2012 年</a>开始做视频游戏解说， <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QGhDCc36ZsI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017 年左右</a>，当虚拟 YouTuber 还在摸索该怎么做时，他开始使用看起来像 MikuMikuDance（MMD）的 3D 模型，并转型为 VTuber。 TheQuillmon 是唯一一位从 VTuber 早期就开始活跃的泰国 VTuber。另外，最近有消息称他隶属于原马来西亚VTuber经纪公司<a href="https://www.myholotv.com/talent/HORI_07" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HØRI07</a>创立的“ <a href="https://virtualzeven.com/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VZ</a> ”。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1007px) 100vw, 1007px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-jpg.webp 1007w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-300x206.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdy5cb7qbh6b-768x527.webp 768w" width="1007" height="691" /></a><br /> <a href="https://vtuberthaiinfo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://vtubethaiinfo.com/</a></p><p>顺便说一下，即使是在泰国，老游戏解说变身VTuber的案例也不少。甚至粉丝们还就泰国VTuber排行榜中应该如何对待经历过这样转世的VTuber展开了激烈争论。</p><p>例如， <a href="https://virtual-youtuber.userlocal.jp/document/ranking" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UserLocal粉丝排行榜</a>上排名靠前的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCompe4fS2oUss8CGTuhOSxA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gibpuri</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGBkYTR4tMKS38TQHGWWLjg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AitoLH</a> ，从2013年开始做视频直播就成为了VTuber。 Gibpuri是一位适合VTuber的YouTuber，早期<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJffGqdKDnc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以现场评论的方式缓慢</a>发帖。</p><h3 id="h.u48nnwyotmsf"> 2019年：企业VTuber先驱“艾莎”横空出世</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.pdes8uk94l1f-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DH0i7g77-jE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DH0i7g77-jE</a></p><p>在泰国VTuber圈子里，你绝对应该知道的就是“Aisha (ไอช่า)”。艾莎是一个以控制生物命运为目的而创造的AI猫形虚拟偶像，出道于动画制作公司<a href="https://www.gaai.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">守护天使艾</a>。她是一名属于公司的VTuber，这在2019年的泰国是很少见的。她热爱K-POP和动漫歌曲，<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdC4e3amqok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">穿着K-POP风格的服装进行3D现场表演</a>，并<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL-DEZKP7bdG5GzaYJ2yIVwkoFDE4LL0A4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">用流利的日语演唱了许多翻唱歌曲</a>。</p><p>我喜欢尝试新事物，我的目标是与不同的品牌合作。例如，我们与泰国游戏《Home Sweet Home: Online》<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NqELyeEZrA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">合作</a>，在日本游戏解说视频中可以看到艾莎的身影。</p><p>在技​​术方面，她在泰国VTuber中尤为出色，曾多次在周年纪念活动中举办<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OOBUouOQU5I" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3D演唱会</a>。这些开创性的努力和技术能力在泰国得到了高度赞扬，我们在“泰国社会奖<a href="https://twitter.com/SocialAwardsTH/status/1496025185626955780" target="_blank" rel="noopener">”的 VTuber 类别中获得了“社交媒体最佳影响力表现”</a> 。</p><h2 id="h.ymonpokffjob">泰国第一家VTuber经纪公司诞生</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-jpg.webp 680w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.2b73jg78gh9g-300x220.webp 300w" width="680" height="499" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/Arcanis_Phriezt/status/1690019193863720961" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/Arcanis_Phriezt/status/1690019193863720961</a></p><p>我还想关注艾莎所属的“<a href="https://www.plg.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">多边形计划</a>”。该机构是由<a href="https://twitter.com/phriezt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">创始人“Phrezt”</a>运营的“ <a href="https://www.matchlink.asia/business/page/Thailand/BANGKOK/79053-polygon-official-company-limited.html#google_vignette" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PolygonOfficial Co.,Ltd</a> ”的一个项目。他们从VTuber活动在泰国开始传播以来就一直活跃，是重点公司之一。艾莎定位为该项目的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W7mKKsnlc-s" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第0代</a>，后续几代均已登场，直至第2代。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-1024x543.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-1024x543.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-300x159.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-768x408.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-1536x815.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.cv2urq2cxegm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="543" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.plg.tv/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.plg.tv/</a></p><p> Polygon Project的第一代成员中，有很多以各种生物为主题的VTuber。例如，Lapine和Lucene以兔子为主题，Zona以虎鲸为主题，Hoku以猫头鹰为主题，Luxia以蝎子为主题，这些作品的设计都很吸引人，深受日本VTuber粉丝的欢迎。这次我想介绍三个我觉得做特别有趣的活动的人。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-1024x380.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-1024x380.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-300x111.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-768x285.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-1536x570.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.d1q0inke2036-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="380" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4a1cJ9Y_X9Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4a1cJ9Y_X9Q</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3HEEdlzT_7c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3HEEdlzT_7c</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h5KYvJWuv_A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h5KYvJWuv_A</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4uyHQIQqnWg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www .youtube.com/watch?v=4uyHQIQqnWg</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZorebMKm5TM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZorebMKm5TM</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_x6FXjEU8ps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_x6FXjEU8ps</a></p><p> “Hoku（โฮคุ）”是一位有着令人印象深刻的笑声和充满活力的声音的VTuber。我们的独特之处在于我们无所畏惧的沟通技巧以及将各国人民联系起来的能力。</p><p>日本 VTuber 机构之间的合作越来越普遍，无论它们是大公司、小公司还是独立公司。然而，Hoku 甚至在这种环境创建之前就拥有成功合作的记录，并且可以被认为是此类合作的先驱之一。</p><p> Hoku 与各种各样的团体合作过，包括崭露头角的独立 VTuber、目前以泰国主要经纪公司而闻名的 Algorhythm Project、印度尼西亚的 MAHA5、以及 Hololive 和 PRISM Project.I am。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-1024x577.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-768x433.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-1536x866.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uuo79bwhdl7k-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="577" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIWR515faEg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIWR515faEg</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dF77Yti2hc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dF77Yti2hc</a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vefV8LsqSU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vefV8LsqSU</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJ0pN_tbfRI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJ0pN_tbfRI</a></p><p> Zona（โซน่า）是一位优秀的歌手，她的突出能力在于她对语言的积极态度。尤其令我惊讶的是，她的第一首原创歌曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIWR515faEg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MEMORIA</a> 》是日语的。</p><p> VTuber是一种起源于日本的文化，因此他们自然与日语文化有联系，例如动漫和歌唱VOCALOID。因此，经常可以看到海外VTuber翻唱日本歌曲。然而，对于原创歌曲来说，选择母国的语言是很常见的，所以 Zona 的选择让我感到惊讶。</p><p>然而，我的想法很快就被驳回了，随后的原创歌曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dF77Yti2hc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BREATHE</a> 》是泰语歌曲，随后发行的《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vefV8LsqSU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">REPRISE</a> 》是一首 K-POP 风格的英文歌曲。这种多样化的音乐表现形式可能反映了泰国是一个文化大熔炉的事实。</p><p>还有一种上传翻译成粉丝母语的翻唱歌曲的文化，例如《星町水生-Stellar Stellar》的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ULduRG1Gp_Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰语翻唱</a>。 Zona对语言的好奇还体现在她愿意用<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJ0pN_tbfRI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">日语翻唱泰国流行的歌曲</a>。</p><p>我认为这些活动不仅仅是营销或策略，而是源于人们的真正兴趣。 Billboard JAPAN的一篇文章称， <a href="https://encount.press/archives/535529/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“有一天，连日语和英语歌词之间的界限都将不再有意义</a>”，而Zona的活动就是这一预测的一个例子。是的。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.1dhvfwo5iop5-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pTh_klItZTA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pTh_klItZTA</a></p><p> “Fumi Hausu (ฟูมิ เฮาสุ)”是一名属于Polygon Project的VTuber，但有着非常独特的背景。 Fumi 最初是作为 Farmhouse 的知识产权 (IP) 诞生的，Farmhouse 是一家<a href="https://www.farmhouse.co.th/company/philosophy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">成立于 1982 年的</a>泰国大型食品公司。这家公司与日本有着密切的联系，销售一种名为“<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-ongjmx7WE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北海道牛奶味面包</a>”的产品，并播放带有日语旁白的<a href="https://www.igloocg.com/portfolio/farmhouse/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3D动画广告</a>。因此，我认为富美在出道时发表诸如“ <a href="https://twitter.com/FumiHausu/status/1487351393854046211" target="_blank" rel="noopener">日本仁木在吗？？？</a> ”等对日本人友好的言论就是在这样的背景下进行的。</p><p>然而，2023 年 1 月，Fumi 突然从该项目毕业。她毕业的原因并不是为了什么糊涂，只是 <a href="https://twitter.com/FumiHausu/status/1615349546225393667" target="_blank" rel="noopener">为了休息和接受新的挑战</a>，同事和粉丝都表示感谢。两个月后，Polygon Project以全新面貌<a href="https://twitter.com/Polygon_Project/status/1639258262984962051" target="_blank" rel="noopener">重新亮相</a>。有趣的是，Farmhouse 仍然使用 FumiHausu IP，并与 Polygon 项目<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GUlznh-H7SY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">保持着良好的关系</a>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-1024x385.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-1024x385.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-300x113.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-768x288.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.fonoowmq3hm9-jpg.webp 1358w" width="1024" height="385" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ZacianVz/status/1713446634330501617" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/ZacianVz/status/1713446634330501617</a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/xKappa_XALTZ/status/1713601686932185091" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/xKappa_XALTZ/status/1713601686932185091</a></p><p> Polygon Project也是一家在泰国积极举办线下活动的机构。例如，在使用标签“ <a href="https://twitter.com/ZonaPLG/status/1706331919108239802" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#PLG3Cha”</a>的三周年歌唱挑战接力项目中，许多VTuber和粉丝唱起了自己喜欢的歌曲，度过了一段愉快的时光。此外，<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7BAU9Y45Zew" target="_blank" rel="noopener">线下演唱会</a>也受到了粉丝们的喜爱，这些活动都取得了成功。</p><h3 id="h.3571s0thvux1"> “芳基债券”连接泰国和日本</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.182b9txjy58g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.182b9txjy58g-1024x512.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.182b9txjy58g-1024x512.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.182b9txjy58g-300x150.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.182b9txjy58g-768x384.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.182b9txjy58g-jpg.webp 1360w" width="1024" height="512" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1642884917003419648" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1642884917003419648</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1715338118109548736" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1715338118109548736</a></p><p>前面我提到泰国是Kizuna AI最先在海外受到关注的国家之一。这种深度联系的一个例子是上述 Polygon 项目 <a href="https://twitter.com/LapinePLG/status/1491749802618490881" target="_blank" rel="noopener">的 Lapine 参与</a>《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GTa2HxIsBPM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kizuna AI The Last Live》你好，世界 2022》</a> 。正如你所看到的，泰国人对Kizuna AI的执着是相当强烈的，这种执着导致了更多不寻常的事情。其原因是，以绊爱为主题的动画《<a href="https://kizunanoallele.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">绊的Aryru</a> 》中，所有泰语配音演员均由泰国VTuber担任。</p><p>泰国的<a href="https://twitter.com/jam_th_official/status/1472559907907911680" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VTuber为动漫配音</a>是有先例的，但令我惊讶的是他们所有的角色都由VTuber来出演。此外，第二季的所有配音演员也都是VTuber。作为一个从一开始就在日本和国外看过 Kizuna AI 和 VTuber 的人，如此大胆地表达敬意的惊喜是最好的。</p><h3 id="h.1291u2ngbokl">已开始使用动画音乐视频的机构</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.t91cybbvg3i0-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="572" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ECm0lLTjZxQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ECm0lLTjZxQ</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VK5HWGOEJlU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VK5HWGOEJlU</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rnTRmG83Qw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rnTRmG83Qw</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kwyDbkZwgTE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www .youtube.com/watch?v=kwyDbkZwgTE</a></p><p>另一个著名的泰国 VTuber 机构是“ <a href="https://www.pixela.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pixela Project</a> ”。该机构由<a href="https://www.matchlink.asia/business/page/Thailand/BANGKOK/43954-pixela-official-co-ltd.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PixelaOfficial Co., Ltd.</a>运营，首席执行官是<a href="https://twitter.com/Atarukun120" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ataru</a> ，他曾管理过 YuChan。</p><p> Pixela Project的独特之处在于，像Hololive和Nijisanji等主要经纪公司一样，他们在乐队出道时发布原创歌曲的音乐视频（MV）。早期以日式动漫人物为主题的明亮有趣氛围的MV较多，但最近以3D空间与2D插画相结合的社交游戏角色为主题的阴暗氛围的MV有所增加。</p><h2 id="h.6xfripi0pcp6">泰国令人兴奋的真实活动：VTuber活动“V-Festa”</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.aa8pnw7pdhw3-768x576.webp 768w" width="800" height="600" /></a><br /> <a href="https://reviewspooh.com/v-festa-review/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://reviewspooh.com/v-festa-review/</a></p><p>虽然这是我个人的看法，但我认为，对于主要从事互联网活动的VTuber来说，线下活动对于在特定国家立足是必不可少的。有机会真正聚在一起享受乐趣，认识到有人与你有相同的兴趣，并体验在一起玩耍的乐趣，这是非常重要的。这也是发现您还不了解的 VTuber 的绝佳机会。</p><p> “V-Festa”是泰国首次举办此类线下活动。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-jpg.webp 900w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-300x142.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vmcqsxox150u-768x364.webp 768w" width="900" height="426" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ShoriNorimaki/status/1484885907262312452" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/ShoriNorimaki/status/1484885907262312452</a></p><p>该活动于2022年1月首次<a href="https://www.thailandtravel.or.jp/central-world/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在泰国首都曼谷的一家购物中心</a>举行。此次见面会的参加者有<a href="https://twitter.com/Ish_mond/status/1484884341448916997" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Aisha、Polygon Project</a> 、Pixela Project<a href="https://twitter.com/7ofumus/status/1484484239143813122" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以及其他当时还不太出名的 VTuber</a> 。另外，在这次活动中，非常有趣的是看到贝月夏尔的原创歌曲模板《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V4L3YuhCUEY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vtuber Q&amp;A自我介绍</a>》被投影在大屏幕上，并 <a href="https://twitter.com/VVinnie12/status/1485141328652804102" target="_blank" rel="noopener">作为VTubers的宣传视频播放</a>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xhvhcezd1iev-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="575" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1586748559411408897" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1586748559411408897</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1660299412231553024" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1660299412231553024</a><a href="https://twitter.com/Beam_haruka/status/1642008494546247680" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/Beam_haruka/status/1642008494546247680</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status/1685130019163803648" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/VFestaTH/status /1685130019163803648</a></p><p>这个活动不是一次性的活动，而是定期举办的，就我个人而言，当我想到泰国的VTuber活动时，我会想到“V-Festa”。一般情况下，这样的活动很难连续举办，但他们之所以能够定期举办，是因为主办方和<a href="https://www.gaai.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">守护天使艾</a>合作<a href="https://www.peerpower.co.th/blog/our-journey-with-shin-a-service" target="_blank" rel="noopener">开发了游戏和流行的市场。泰国文化。这是因为它是由“SHIN-A Service”<a href="https://reviewspooh.com/v-festa-review/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">赞助的</a></a>。</p><h2 id="h.xm30azgxcfw2">泰国著名的 VTuber 有哪些？</h2><p>在这里，我们将介绍泰国当前VTuber文化中不可忽视的VTuber，并详细解释他们是如何活跃的。</p><h3 id="h.hdjyqljlzgwe">独立 VTuber 的崛起：Laibaht 掌握了他的声音</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vnpb5itf96rh-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="572" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xrWLzhw8inY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xrWLzhw8inY</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nb1fNtfBpj0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nb1fNtfBpj0</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=egbo6T_toXY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=egbo6T_toXY</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ph6h5xmaRcQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www .youtube.com/watch?v=ph6h5xmaRcQ</a></p><p>在泰国的VTuber行业中，有一些令人惊叹的人是通过个人活动而不是团体活动登上明星舞台的。 “ <a href="https://twitter.com/manyvproject" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Manybaht V Project</a> ”所属的“Laibaht (หลายบาท)”就是其中之一。 Laibaht 凭借他的声音和幽默而广受欢迎，他专注于稍微大胆的 ASMR、创作基于模因的视频并模仿流行人物的声音。他们还发行翻唱歌曲，我个人最喜欢的是《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ph6h5xmaRcQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我唱最好的九月》，</a>这是《土风火九月》的翻唱。在这首歌中，你可以感受到Laibaht的阳光、可爱、幽默。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-1024x271.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-1024x271.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-300x80.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-768x204.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-1536x407.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.okb773qvv9g-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="271" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1608464140879945728" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1608464140879945728</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326081329524737" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326081329524737</a></p><p>支持广告是衡量 VTuber 受欢迎程度的指标之一。随着 K-POP 的兴起，应援广告已在全球范围内传播，已<a href="https://premium.kai-you.net/article/717" target="_blank" rel="noopener">成为 VTuber 生日庆祝活动中的固定内容</a>。这种文化在泰国已经很普遍，“MBK中心”的大屏幕上有时会显示VTuber<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1608464140879945728" target="_blank" rel="noopener">应援广告</a>。</p><p>餐厅也会举办合作活动，<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326081329524737" target="_blank" rel="noopener">设立真人大小的展板</a>，<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1636326099230822401" target="_blank" rel="noopener">分发限量版商品</a>，并提供其他形式的支持。除此之外，莱巴特还担任翻译配音演员，在《Paripi Komei》中饰演<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1589582718308081666" target="_blank" rel="noopener">女主角月见英子</a>，在《忍之子》中<a href="https://twitter.com/manybaht/status/1666440826451378186" target="_blank" rel="noopener">饰演有马假名</a>。</p><h3 id="h.qtb2saxpbx9i">扩展到电子竞技领域：Dtto 在职业游戏团队之间流动。</h3><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.anrzbwd28102-1-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3_nt4dN6gA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3_nt4dN6gA</a></p><p>三语VTuber“Dtto.”是活跃于APEX Legends等FPS游戏的国际VTuber。出道时隶属于日本职业游戏战队“SCARZ”，<a href="https://www.scarz.net/news/cc_230915/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">合同到期</a>后暂时<a href="https://twitter.com/_dtto/status/1750479822386844148" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以独立人身份加入“REJECT”</a> 。</p><p>他曾与Haru Shibuya和Hololive的Laplace Darkness合作，在日本广为人知。另外，由于以泰语发行，因此在泰国也得到了很多粉丝的支持。她还<a href="https://twitter.com/Maruya_Event/status/1599773249877200902" target="_blank" rel="noopener">受邀</a>参加了活跃在泰国的VTuber参加的线下活动“MARUYA”，可见她在泰国的知名度有多么高。</p><p>除了FPS游戏之外，我从开始VTuber活动之前就一直在发布自己唱歌的视频，其中一首《 <a href="https://youtu.be/HQ1zA2bbIRU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Glare</a> 》，声音好听，声音独特，听后有一种愉悦的感觉，推荐。</p><h3 id="h.ytoqdtiw2jne">进军音乐界：Unnämed 用与灵魂共鸣的声音歌唱</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.dx26rd9qn16u-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gBNlpDTGck" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gBNlpDTGck</a></p><p>在泰国VTuber乐坛背景下，一位不可忽视的歌手就是“Unnämed（U-san）”。他们的许多原创歌曲和翻唱歌曲有力而细腻，其中许多歌曲的演唱充满情感，他们继续通过音乐吸引世界各地的歌迷。</p><p>我特别推荐<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gBNlpDTGck" target="_blank" rel="noopener">翻唱歌曲</a>《Ado - Dance (Odo)》，这是与ARP的Dacapo合作的。这首歌最大的魅力在于，实力派歌手们用声音互相较量，真是太酷了。</p><p>另外，原曲的音乐录影带原本是关于拳击的，但被编排成了泰拳世界观。这是对总部位于泰国的ARP的尊重的表达，也可能是受到U-san在<a href="https://www.dexerto.com/entertainment/unnamed-feature-u-san-vtuber-restart-2480915/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">采访</a>中提到的泰国根源的影响。</p><h2 id="h.94p14bb0fvfc">泰国最受欢迎的VTuber团体“算法计划（ARP）”是什么？</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.vr8w748h5mo9-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw</a></p><p> VTuber粉丝中，也有追随小众的粉丝。其中之一就是<a href="https://note.com/mikan_ito" target="_blank" rel="noopener">热爱VTuber音乐的</a><a href="https://note.com/mikan_ito" target="_blank" rel="noopener">粉丝</a>，某个机构的音乐开始吸引<a href="https://note.com/showyoutaro/n/ndc5deed51bc3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这些疯狂VTuber音乐爱好者的传感器</a>。</p><p>该机构的名称是“<a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">算法项目</a>（ARP）”。</p><p>我本人对VTuber的音乐并不是像发烧友那样热情，但2022<a href="https://note.com/bluesura/n/n895d48b172bb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">年我在国内和国际都沉浸在VTuber的音乐中</a>。特别是，我仍然记得来自 ARP 的 Solar 的“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Solar feat.@Selene_ARP – Dawn</a> ”的震撼。她的歌声让我想起了虚拟歌手“Kafu”，她的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tMKrECxEpq8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声音充满力量，似乎在攻击我的情绪</a>。另一件让我写出情感句子的事情是细节动画的高度原创性。</p><p>截至2022年，已经有很多VTuber歌曲的优质MV。 Hololive发布了《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vV-5W7SFHDc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">凤翔Marine – 我是你的宝藏盒</a>》等精美动画MV，虹山寺发布了《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=53jm_c2FMjw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vox Akuma – New Cydonia</a> 》等精美动画MV，“ <a href="https://kamitsubaki.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO</a> ”则创作了详细的世界观。以富有创造力而闻名。不过，看到一家在海外名不见经传的公司突然推出这么有能量的MV，真是让人起鸡皮疙瘩。更值得关注的是，不知为何，这支MV中包含了“日文翻译歌词”，成为了一部非常耐人寻味的作品。</p><h3 id="h.19hzvwcgk7rv"> “算法节奏计划”用音乐的力量开辟新路径</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-jpg.webp 680w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.7hoca8gh7k8b-300x188.webp 300w" width="680" height="426" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1367474401587863555" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1367474401587863555</a></p><p>拥有自己语言的文化地区有植根于该地区的独特音乐文化。正如日本有 J-POP、韩国有 K-POP 一样，泰国也有自己的流派，称为 T-POP。泰国的音乐界是一个传统音乐备受关注的国家，但新一代音乐也拥有强大的音乐存在感，播放量达数亿次。<a href="https://birthdayadjp.shop/blogs/birthday-ads/thai-ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国艺人活跃在 K-POP 领域</a>的事实表明了他们的潜力。</p><p> ARP 是一家在泰国持续发展的公司。该项目由“ <a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Realic Production Co., Ltd.</a> ”管理，其理念是“<a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/company/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我们是创意人。我们将创作泰国人民从未见过的原创作品，例如虚拟Youtuber、音乐视频、动作漫画等。” “创造你的作品，实现你的梦想和想象力。</a> ”</p><p> ARP这个名字来源于“算法”和“节奏”两个词的组合，代表了公司通过音乐节奏实现各种目标的愿望。除了音乐之外，拥有独特才能的成员们的直播也让现场气氛更加热闹。</p><h2 id="h.qjre8r7bs8mc"> ARP 与其他 VTuber 机构有何不同？</h2><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-jpg.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-300x90.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.i5p87xaq7yuo-768x230.webp 768w" width="1024" height="306" /></a><br /> <a href="https://algorhythm.realic.net/members" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://algorhythm.realic.net/members</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/LapisJellyF_ARP" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/LapisJellyF_ARP</a></p><p>在VTuber行业中，以开放形式举行选秀并增加附属人才数量的趋势很强烈。然而，ARP 的独特之处在于<a href="https://pantip.com/topic/41928029" target="_blank" rel="noopener">它与此约定完全相反</a>。 ARP 不会进行大规模的试镜，而是 <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1570409854053023744" target="_blank" rel="noopener">直接从已经与其代理机构有关系或有某种联系的创作者那里物色人才</a>。</p><p>也许是因为这样的管理政策，成员之间的纽带非常牢固，团队合作的品质贯穿始终。 ARP 即将进入运营的第四个年头，迄今为止，还没有一个成员离开该机构。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 922px) 100vw, 922px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-jpg.webp 922w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-300x151.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.esabrnnmca22-768x387.webp 768w" width="922" height="465" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CbH6mUVPiw</a></p><p>另一个特点是ARP成员在音乐制作上积极协作。</p><p>例如，ARP的首支动漫风格MV《黎明》，出道后的VTube和VTuber分别负责作曲、编曲、声乐剪辑、混音、母带、和声、字幕、日文翻译和英文翻译，不包括视频制作，我在服务。而且，评论区的成员们都非常感动，足见他们为发行这部作品倾注了极大的热情。</p><h3 id="h.yxjxd1rufbby">从音乐录影带看出泰国手绘动画制作的成熟</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-jpg.webp 600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.24oxbnmxzmlb-300x240.webp 300w" width="600" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhbpyfesrhQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhbpyfesrhQ</a></p><p>我提到ARP的特点之一是音乐视频的手绘风格动画，但是这个动画是从哪里来的呢？</p><p>首先，泰国细胞动画和CG（计算机图形）动画有着悠久的历史，可以追溯到20世纪50年代。 Payut Ngaokrachang据说是<a href="https://artsandculture.google.com/story/payut-ngao-krachang-father-of-thai-animation-thai-film-archive/sAXhQtVXnGgZWQ?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰国细胞动画电影的先驱</a>。 Payut先生在日本学习动画，并为赛璐珞动画设计了自己的相机支架。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w3k7bcv6ng4e-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FF5vbODeHdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FF5vbODeHdk</a></p><p>然而，据我们调查，手绘动画在泰国的发展程度，并没有太多值得关注的作品。事实上，CG动画似乎正在增长。这只是我的猜测，但我认为这是因为泰国的动漫市场过去一直不稳定，而且因为泰国作为动漫采购的主要来源地，受到了日本以外的外国公司的强大影响。最近，东宝以总承包商而非分包商的身份<a href="https://www.nikkei.com/nkd/disclosure/tdnr/20231102578098/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">投资</a>了<a href="https://www.igloocg.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IGLOO STUDIO</a> ，该公司根据 Netflix 上的日本原创小说制作 3D 动画，也引起了日本国内的关注。</p><p>低廉的劳动力成本是泰国动画产业成为外包强国的原因之一。不过，据称主要原因是泰国政府正在积极吸引外国企业， <a href="https://www.absoluteanime.com/articles/how-thai-animators-have-helped-japans-anime-industry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">放宽对动漫领域外资持股的限制</a>。此外， <a href="https://sponsored.bloomberg.com/article/boi/creative-spark-ignites-thailands-digital-advance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">数字经济促进局（DEPA）正在推动数字化</a>，这带动了动漫和游戏产业的大幅增长。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-1024x492.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-1024x492.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-300x144.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-768x369.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.8m9hizomo483-jpg.webp 1238w" width="1024" height="492" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/saratowga/status/1732637626237333706" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/saratowga/status/1732637626237333706</a></p><p>与日本的职业学校一样<a href="https://www.spu.ac.th/digitalmedia/programs/animation-and-visualeffects/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">，泰国的大学也提供CG动画专业课程</a>。作为该计划的一部分，我们邀请活跃在各自专业领域的工程师担任客座讲师，与学生分享实践知识。当然，负责ARPMV动画的主创们也在曼谷历史悠久的斯里巴吞大学进行了 <a href="https://twitter.com/saratowga/status/1732637626237333706" target="_blank" rel="noopener">演讲</a>。</p><p>为 ARP 创作动画的才华横溢的创作者有好几位，特别是曾担任 Evalia 的《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f_gN2-_UZIs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">无尽回声》</a>视频导演的泰国动画师 KAGO，在日本动画界有着良好的业绩。我在这里。 2023年，KAGO还担任<a href="https://twitter.com/_kakakakago/status/1742326082429456848" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《偶像大师灰姑娘女孩》的主要动画师（原创动画）</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/_kakakakago/status/1737803716026364337" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《乌玛娘Pretty Derby》的动画导演。</a></p><p> ARP 发行的 50 多首原创歌曲中，有 10 多首有手绘动画，参与制作的泰国创作者逐渐增多，KAGO 等人创建了名为「<a href="https://twitter.com/_kakakakago/status/1755694947972567086" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANIMETIX</a> 」的工作室，专门从事动画。它已经发展到这样的规模，已经建立了一个</p><h3 id="h.1bv4vz2dcjxl">支持 ARP 基金会的首席执行官“REAL”对内容充满热情</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-1024x369.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-1024x369.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-300x108.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-768x277.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-1536x554.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.miyy8v3lgzy2-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="369" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1610639907843723264" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1610639907843723264</a><br /> <a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=WmEOkpC6IrQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://youtube.com/watch?v=WmEOkpC6IrQ</a></p><p>支持ARP的核心人物之一是Realic Production公司的首席执行官“ <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">REAL</a> ”。被ARP成员昵称为“红鸭子”，经常在Twitter上被取笑，<a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=WmEOkpC6IrQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">出现在音乐视频中</a>，并被用作<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BVA1c7fPfCg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">浪漫的合作伙伴项目</a>，表明他是一个深受喜爱的角色。我听得出来。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uvtzmu8rlj9x-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uvtzmu8rlj9x-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uvtzmu8rlj9x-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uvtzmu8rlj9x-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uvtzmu8rlj9x-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.uvtzmu8rlj9x-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dC2gJncUcrU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dC2gJncUcrU</a></p><p>另一方面，REAL深入参与了<a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1610639907843723264" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ARP厂牌的歌词</a>等世界观的创作，并且作为创作者也很活跃。在《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NXvPkzF8pI8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">V-MATSURI</a> 》中，REAL本人展现了自己优美的嗓音，并为纪念ARP成立一周年，与朋友们一起演唱了《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dC2gJncUcrU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我的歌词</a>》，写下了对ARP的感情，感动了很多粉丝。</p><p> REAL 的座右铭是“ <a href="https://twitter.com/ARP_Vtuber/status/1610639907843723264" target="_blank" rel="noopener">创造有趣的作品，然后死去</a>。”从这句话中可以看出，他将一生的精力都倾注在了创作和ARP上。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ixq6pkyi2bb9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ixq6pkyi2bb9-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ixq6pkyi2bb9-jpg.webp 577w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ixq6pkyi2bb9-204x300.webp 204w" width="577" height="847" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/realofficial_th/status/1729088001672978761" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/realofficial_th/status/1729088001672978761</a></p><p> Mr. REAL不仅是一位创意人才，更是一位热爱本土文化的人。在泰国，有一个节日叫“水灯节”，在满月之夜举行，以表达对河神的感激和歉意。当天，REAL和ARP成员就自己的音乐作品向女神表达了感谢、歉意和坚定的决心。</p><p>这种强烈的感觉引发了当天发行的音乐作品的热议。</p><h2 id="h.yorlccualc0i">从ARP至今的历史看VTuber文化的崛起</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xa40zie7ozmr-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://algor-arcana.eventpassinsight.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://algor-arcana.eventpassinsight.co/</a></p><p> ARP有两条路线：一条供独立VTuber的单独加入，另一个可以进行小组首次亮相。小组的首次亮相有两种类型：一个是让小组具有特定的主题，另一个是在真实创建的故事中作为角色首次亮相。</p><h3 id="h.2xlvqvts073x"> 2021年4月：Vtuber项目始于摸索</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypq6iy2naup-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypq6iy2naup-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypq6iy2naup-jpg.webp 854w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypq6iy2naup-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypq6iy2naup-768x432.webp 768w" width="854" height="480" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zE_5EfY4pNk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ze_5efy4pnk</a></p><p> ARP首次亮相的第一个小组是一个叙事结构，称为“第一行动启示录”。它由一个废墟的幸存者组成，充满了绝望，它融合了不同的世界观，例如“ Asteroth”，《 Atteroth》，来世的龙之王“ evalia”，banshee，banshee，将灵魂引导到黑社会和“ S1R”，一个陌生人， Android秘密警察部队。它是由看起来像这样的角色组成的。当时，现实情况尚未建立为一家公司，因此我相信它具有强烈的挑战性态度。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-1024x768.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-1024x768.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-768x576.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.erllymaouqbx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="768" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/7ofumus/status/1484484239143813122" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/7ofumus/status/1484484239143813122</a></p><p> ARP的早期角色模型是Live2D，具有刚起步和摸索的感觉。尽管如此，可以看出，从那时起，粉丝群就有很强的粉丝群，而且期望很高。但是，从2021年到2022年，泰国VTUBER社区是一个小型的VTUBER市场，与讲英语的国家，中国和印度尼西亚相比，它仍在增长<a href="https://droidsans.com/youtube-super-chat-super-stickers-super-thanks-available-thailand/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">，尚未实施超级钟</a>，因此有许多障碍要克服。但是，在热情的粉丝的支持下，ARP逐渐发展成为当前的精致风格。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-1024x438.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-1024x438.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-300x128.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-768x328.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-1536x657.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.xfl86pmf6qzm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="438" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0JabuKg-1U" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0jabukg-1u</a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dufWaRfhfDI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dufwarfhfdi</a></p><p>评估是ARP的中心人物。在直播期间，他像莲花一样绽放着灿烂的笑容，尽管他似乎有点自信，但他还是情绪化的制造商，他用嬉戏的笑话来嘲笑成员，并在氛围中生气。在溪流中，您可以看到他们在喝酒并喝醉时做塔罗牌的命运和聊天。她是一个vtuber，每一步都很可爱。可爱的。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.qmbo7ig8f3hk-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.qmbo7ig8f3hk-1024x580.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.qmbo7ig8f3hk-1024x580.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.qmbo7ig8f3hk-300x170.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.qmbo7ig8f3hk-768x435.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.qmbo7ig8f3hk-jpg.webp 1059w" width="1024" height="580" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_wDhqdMYDgI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_wdhqdmydgi</a></p><p>此外，我们拥有ARP代理商中少数几个3D模型之一，我们使用它们来广播现场表演和VRCHAT。尽管泰国<a href="https://www.jetro.go.jp/biz/areareports/special/2021/0301/174331ac3d38afb4.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在投资数字技术方面</a>取得了进展，但IT领域正在迅速发展，该国正在朝着比日本更先进的无现金社会发展，但在基础设施方面仍然有些领域不足。实际上，我们有时会看到 <a href="https://twitter.com/Evalia_ARP/status/1575090539695058945" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一些ARP成员由于基础设施问题而被迫暂停分配的案例</a>。因此，在日本和讲英语的国家中很常见的3D流媒体仍然是泰国Vtuber场景中的罕见类别。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u7eiljop1p9f-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u7eiljop1p9f-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u7eiljop1p9f-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u7eiljop1p9f-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u7eiljop1p9f-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.u7eiljop1p9f-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hFzGIEoTAYI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hfzgieotayi</a></p><p> Evalia的音乐活动也是她的景点之一。这首歌使我意识到它的魅力是“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hFzGIEoTAYI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">แค่แค่（龙舌兰酒）</a> ”。这首歌是在黎明发行一个月后发布的。</p><p>这首歌的作品是Evalia的沉思唱歌声，时尚的声音以及彼此相撞的冷冰节奏舒适，创造了一种非常适合饮酒的喜怒无常的氛围。它使Evalia的成人魅力充满了。</p><p>我也非常尊重Evalia对音乐的态度。当Evalia在推特上发布了主题曲“ Loony”的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C1h3MpDg8yc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">泰语版本</a>“副社会”时，她收到了卡车制造商Kouta的评论，并用引用了一句话，而Evalia则用手示意了“ <a href="https://twitter.com/Evalia_ARP/status/1712581235107868948" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我喜欢这首歌”的信息！</a>礼貌地。在当今自动翻译发展的时代，这种态度非常动人。</p><h3 id="h.x1vq9lxstvit"> 2021年9月：与团体扩展和品牌斗争的可见斗争</h3><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.3xqwfsueqza0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.3xqwfsueqza0-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.3xqwfsueqza0-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.3xqwfsueqza0-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.3xqwfsueqza0-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.3xqwfsueqza0-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cLLX_uuNrhI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cllx_uunrhi</a></p><p>接下来，出现了四人单位“第二行动Eclipse”：月球女王“ Selene”，成为太阳大师“太阳能”的女孩，文明的最高领导人“ Zekai”和流星男孩徘徊着世界。随着“顶峰”，该小组开始有一些团结。特别有趣的是，与故事的设置不同，成员获得了诸如“虚拟歌手（Vsinger）”之类的标题。这似乎是该机构不断扩大的努力，以找到一种平衡故事及其成员个性的方法的结果。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypmonwd4i8go-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypmonwd4i8go-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypmonwd4i8go-jpg.webp 710w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.ypmonwd4i8go-300x229.webp 300w" width="710" height="542" /></a><br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/bluesura/status/1675120597897191425" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://twitter.com/bluesura/status/1675120597897191425</a></p><p>我想将Solar作为该单元的值得注意的成员介绍。她的歌声以强大的人声和情感为特征，从她的可爱外观中很难想象。她还非常流利地唱着日语歌曲。许多ARP成员可以唱日本歌曲，但Solar的表演特别敏锐。</p><p>歌曲的选择主要是充满活力的封面歌曲，例如Ado和Lisa。在“ Cosplay Art Festival（CAF）2023”中，Solar热情地<a href="https://youtu.be/jvboZy4-Hz0?t=187" target="_blank" rel="noopener">唱着</a>“ Kanzaki Iori-生活讨厌我”，这是一首太阳能具有很强依恋的歌曲。此外，在定期举行的慈善音乐会“ Arparty”中，他们可爱地表演“ Kafu-吃了过去”，同时<a href="https://www.youtube.com/live/HDPlWNYIbo8?t=841" target="_blank" rel="noopener">使用Live2D重现了Hanafuda台阶</a>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w9y3pivsx7c4-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w9y3pivsx7c4-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea196086e2ee1c69d87a9c2a9-kix.w9y3pivsx7c4-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f8f3a08ea19608